          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎认出大唐朝取经三藏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "柏宪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下官有眼无珠，多有得罪。大圣既能救令师返本还原，必知小女下落。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙悟空 （小梁州） 俺在那黄金塔院会红妆，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是君家爱女堪伤。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "常把归期望，盼亲舍，泪千行。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（柏宪哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙悟空 （么篇） 你不念亲生骨肉遭魔，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一谜价蛊惑妖王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "柏宪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我那儿苦煞你了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙悟空 （么篇） 你何必假慈想，空惆怅，"
        },
        {
          "character": "柏宪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣僧，下官知罪了！令徒处，望乞方便。令我父女早得团圆，莫大恩德。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "悟空，他的令嫒，你可救她一救。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父，那百花羞呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（么篇） 俺提出了天罗地网。"
        },
        {
          "character": "柏宪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "几时得？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙悟空 （么篇） 顷刻里便知端详。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（猪悟能、百花羞、花香洁、闻仁同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了。请开眼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花羞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是哪里了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那个不是你的父亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那个不是你女儿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "柏宪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然是我女儿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "百花羞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "柏宪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此女是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这就是受冤枉闻道泉的妻子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你二人过来，见过大将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "柏宪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下官得罪。闻娘子同小女到府中相会寒荆。闻生随下官入朝，奏明圣上。定当"
        },
        {
          "character": "柏宪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一力保奏，管取荣华。前者受惊，下官着实抱疚了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（车夫上，百花羞、花香洁、车夫同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "柏宪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大圣，有劳神力，令我父女团圆。下官何以为报？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大将军！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 今朝喜得花无恙，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "笑杀邻家蝶自忙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "结果了两下悽怆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八戒，沙僧，随师父进朝去见国王。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 俺再去剪妖狼，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "才不负孙爷爷重下降！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人自两边分下。）"
        }
      ],
